240	                "rbtd: unknown fixture '{}' — not registered in manifest",
241	                fixture
242	            ));
243	        }
244	    };
245	    for colophon in required {
246	        let found = manifest.split_whitespace().any(|token| token == *colophon);
247	        if !found {
248	            return Err(format!(
249	                "rbtd: colophon '{}' not found in zipper manifest (fixture '{}')",
250	                colophon, fixture
251	            ));
252	        }
253	    }
254	    Ok(())
255	}
